title: Bruce Feldman on the State of College Football
itunes:title: Bruce Feldman on the State of College Football
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode. To start off, the guys are joined by college football reporter and insider Bruce Feldman as he discusses the possibilities of spring college football, how colleges are adjusting to the pandemic and the potential impact everything can have on student athletes (:46). To wrap up the show, DJ and Bucky react to the main points from the interview with Bruce Feldman (43:11).
